<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/4 (50 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Charge.</em></strong> If the ox moves at least 20 feet straight toward a target and then hits it with a gore attack on the same turn, the target takes an extra 7 (2d6) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Beast of Burden.</em></strong> The oxen is considered to be a Huge animal for the purposes of determining its carrying capacity.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Gore.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 7 (1d6+4) piercing damage.</p>

